{"tid":823483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌的士佬收貴車錢嘅都係自私到極 最垃撚圾嘅人種","createTime":"2018-09-16T23:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T04:56:54.000Z","uid":18720,"like":13,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c4e25235a082955619d5719aa4ceb7a5ac3c9b7e","tid":823483,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T23:13:12.000Z","msg":"成班戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當8號風以上所有交通工具停晒之後<br />\n仲敢玩命嘅的士佬所提供嘅根本可以被列入係緊急服務<br />\n<br />\n班死窮撚睇怕都未必有裝uber app<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過喺旺區叫車就明<br />\nincrease demand情況下uber經常加價加幾成 double都見過<br />\n咁又點？明買明賣 <br />\n你坐就咪撚屌 屌就咪撚坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加價加到咁咪有效令到唔係咁趕急嘅人選擇其他方式嘅交通 咁咪可以抑制個流量去返合理水平囉<br />\n市場機制自然嘅調節嚟<br />\n<br />\n至於的士佬玩命 保險唔包等等<br />\n有10萬個人都講過 我就唔重覆喇<br />\n<br />\n如果你本身有車 咁點解你唔揸車？你嘅風險就係風險 人地嘅風險就唔撚係風險？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你冇車 咁事態真係緊急嘅 你都唔撚會慳呢幾舊水啦<br />\n呢幾舊水重要啲嘅話 咁件事都唔需要緊張啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你賤命一條咋 <br />\n爆玻璃閒閒地幾千<br />\n車廂爛左穿左都唔識點計<br />\n<br />\n至於你話打風要出街飲茶嗰啲<br />\n我屌爆你地老母 自食惡果抵撚死<br />\n<br />\n要搭的士返工嗰啲<br />\nwell paid嘅的士錢100%有得claim啦 根本風度嚟<br />\n冇得claim嗰啲都係垃圾工種 你程的士都分分鐘貴過你日薪 咁你返去托柒呀？咁都出warning嘅話你仲返呢份工？你狗嚟嫁！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁撚威嘅咪買定架單車喺屋企囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc885d670efe268f4e599c628467bfe2f14e921d","tid":823483,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T23:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a8f67515a8feef0d784dd992669ffce7c584580","tid":823483,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T23:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6bf6c21ff0e3815857087fcaa81710a4a8319e","tid":823483,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T23:23:09.000Z","msg":"靜雞雞負評嗰啲死垃圾仲唔喇喇臨游水返工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日狗鐵開左大部分呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c32b7a02631916597041a7e86a5792978345c8c9","tid":823483,"uid":18720,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T23:28:04.000Z","msg":"啲賤種死死氣留負評但駁唔撚到呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6e7fda499b44d43fd3ce6d96afadbb9bd8974a","tid":823483,"uid":18720,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T23:35:00.000Z","msg":"成班死垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講好價錢先上車 又唔係落車先劏鳩你<br />\n<br />\n比得起錢而件事真係十萬火急嘅大有人在<br />\n你嫌貴嘅大把人狗衝"},{"pid":"79ce2379237b1a6bc861d8c2922f0472f53437b5","tid":823483,"uid":18720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T23:43:46.000Z","msg":"笑柒你班輸打贏要嘅垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeddee67403fcbeec372aa4e2a1ab8b4f4aaddc8","tid":823483,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d4a9bef3efde04dc5b982ff5d184d2e7534607","tid":823483,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T04:56:54.000Z","msg":"班死窮撚喺大圍賴左屎未呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}